data.description: Your view of the lake calls you home to watch a sunset, throw a party for family and friends or simply enjoy the view.  Original owner refreshed this '06 charmer with luxury vinyl plank flooring, interior paint and a new roof.  Open floor plan connects kitchen with the family room. On those chilly nights focus on the fireplace stoked with gas logs.  Upstairs a huge game room ringed by three ample bedrooms.   First floor master ensuite looks out over the beautiful lake.  Washer & Dryer included, just bring your own refrigerator.  All that's needed now is for you to create what you want in the backyard, to enjoy the view of the lake.
